@startuml
title Plane State Transition Diagram

initial : Initial State

state Order {
    state Arrived
    state Prepared
    state Operational
    state Maintained
    state OutOfService
    state Withdrawn

    initial --> Arrived : Arrival
}

Arrived --> Prepared : Arrival

Prepared --> Operational : Assignment to Operations
Prepared --> Maintained : Assignment to Maintenance

Operational --> Maintained : No Scheduled Flights or Maintenance Required

Maintained --> Prepared : Service Completed

Prepared --> OutOfService : Plane Not Available for Use
Operational --> Withdrawn : Permanent Withdrawal from Service

@enduml
